protected void assertPlanHash(QueryPlanner planner, RecordQueryPlan plan, PlanHashable.PlanHashKind kind, int expectedOriginalHash, int expectedCascadesHash)  
to the test base class
Convert each @DualPlannerTest  assert block from

        assertEquals(-447322749, plan2.planHash(PlanHashable.PlanHashKind.LEGACY));
